From: L. David Baron <dbaron@dbaron.org>

Bug 960465 patch N - Part 2 of switching from posting restyle for animation to immediately restyling:  Stop posting a restyle for animation when we start transitions.

This makes the way we start transitions more like the way we start
animations.

